   DISK VIEWER  -  Settings Page
   /plugins/diskviewer/DiskViewerSettings.page

   Copyright (C) 2026 Lazaros Chalkidis
   License: GPLv3

   Renders Settings > Utilities > Disk Viewer Settings. Handles its own
   POST submission (write diskviewer.cfg) and emits the form HTML plus
   the inline JavaScript that wires AJAX apply, reset-to-defaults, and
   the credits modal.

   Section ordering:
     1. Server-side: sanitizers, POST handler, defaults, theme, version
     2. Style includes & FOUC suppression
     3. Top credits link
     4. Form helpers (toggle closures)
     5. Settings panel sections (Behavior / Display / Header / Spin)
     6. Action bar (Apply / Reset / Done)
     7. Footer row (support + version)
     8. Credits modal markup
     9. Inline JavaScript (section collapse, AJAX apply, reset, modal)
